### Get products
GET http://localhost:5200/api/products?skip=0&take=5
Accept: application/json

### Search products by keyword
GET http://localhost:5200/api/products?q=Ryzen
Accept: application/json

### Get product details
GET http://localhost:5200/api/products/1
Accept: application/json

### Price history
GET http://localhost:5200/api/products/1/price-history?bucket=day&from={{from}}&to={{to}}
Accept: application/json

### Recommendations
GET http://localhost:5200/api/products/1/recommendations?take=5
Accept: application/json

### Track view
POST http://localhost:5200/api/track/view
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "sessionId": "demo-session",
  "userId": 42
}

### Validate PC
POST http://localhost:5200/api/pc/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cpuId": 2,
  "motherboardId": 1,
  "ramId": 2,
  "gpuId": 1,
  "psuId": 2,
  "caseId": 2,
  "coolerId": 1,
  "storageIds": [2,3]
}

### Auto build PC
POST http://localhost:5200/api/pc/autobuild
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "budget": 1500,
  "priorities": ["gaming"],
  "platform": "amd"
}

### Admin upsert product
POST http://localhost:5200/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "sku": "CPU-5600X",
  "name": "AMD Ryzen 5 5600X",
  "categoryId": 1,
  "price": 239.99,
  "attributes": "{\"componentType\":\"cpu\",\"componentId\":1}"
}

### Analytics co-purchase
GET http://localhost:5200/api/analytics/top-copurchases?take=10
Accept: application/json

### Analytics top views
GET http://localhost:5200/api/analytics/top-views?take=10
Accept: application/json

### List product reviews
GET http://localhost:5200/api/products/1/reviews?skip=0&take=10&order=createdAt
Accept: application/json

