### Request presigned upload (user)
POST http://localhost:5200/api/uploads/presign
Authorization: Bearer {{userJwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "extension": "jpg",
  "contentType": "image/jpeg",
  "maxFileSize": 5000000,
  "purpose": "reviews"
}

### Upload product image (admin)
